ikh bin dokh a patriotke far Yisroel

00:11:23.601 --> 00:11:25.164
iz dokh avade gut."

00:11:25.356 --> 00:11:29.206
un mir hobn ongehoybn shoyn etlekhe verter lernen zikh shoyn oyf IVRIT

00:11:29.206 --> 00:11:30.766
tsugreytn a bisl

00:11:31.853 --> 00:11:34.614
ikh likvidir mayn gesheft

00:11:35.532 --> 00:11:36.758
ikh UNK

00:11:37.523 --> 00:11:39.170
aynkoyfn far zikh

00:11:39.953 --> 00:11:42.006
tsu firn in Yisroel

00:11:43.446 --> 00:11:45.822
vayl in Poyln iz geven rekht

00:11:45.822 --> 00:11:48.030
zeyer a sakh vos aroystsufirn.

00:11:49.217 --> 00:11:52.012
tsum bayshpil, oyb ikh hob gehat keylim

00:11:52.255 --> 00:11:54.004
hob ikh gemegt firn

00:11:55.410 --> 00:11:59.893
fleyshike, milkhike, pareve, un peysekhdike.

00:12:00.996 --> 00:12:02.492
azoy iz geven

00:12:03.308 --> 00:12:05.428
keylim, in tep

00:12:05.485 --> 00:12:07.352
un in farsheydene keylim.

00:12:09.028 --> 00:12:12.093
kh'hob gekoyft naye mebl, ersht fun gesheft

00:12:13.382 --> 00:12:17.159
vayle ikh hob ge- gants gut fardint, vayl handl iz

00:12:17.159 --> 00:12:19.538
UNK gants gut, iz dokh an eygener gesheft

00:12:19.538 --> 00:12:21.763
gut, kh'hob getsolt shtayern

00:12:23.878 --> 00:12:26.167
avekgegebn di dire

00:12:26.173 --> 00:12:29.491
der melukhe. dem gesheft hob ikh farshlosn

00:12:31.422 --> 00:12:34.352
mayne poyerim vos lebn in Poyln

00:12:35.421 --> 00:12:37.679
vos zaynen gekumen fun Vaysrusland

00:12:37.679 --> 00:12:39.399
oykh emigrirt keyn Poyln

00:12:39.399 --> 00:12:41.629
un ikh hob mit zey gehat a gute kontakt

00:12:41.629 --> 00:12:44.274
zaynen gekumen tsu mir, az zey hobn tsugenumen

00:12:44.314 --> 00:12:46.012
alts fun gesheft

00:12:46.356 --> 00:12:47.930
vos iz geblibn

00:12:47.930 --> 00:12:49.120
di vog

00:12:49.120 --> 00:12:51.660
groyse un kleyne vos shteyt oyfn tish

00:12:51.958 --> 00:12:53.892
oyf a frizhider

00:12:55.215 --> 00:12:57.195
iz geven bay mir in gesheft.

00:12:57.195 --> 00:12:59.001
alts hobn zay bay mir tsugenumen.

00:12:59.001 --> 00:13:00.171
fun shtub

00:13:00.548 --> 00:13:01.706
di mebl

00:13:01.898 --> 00:13:05.824
alts hob ikh zey gegebn, zaynen geblibn gute fraynt AD HAYOM.

00:13:06.083 --> 00:13:07.629
biz hayntikn tog.

00:13:08.530 --> 00:13:10.684
mir kumen in Erets Yisroel

00:13:10.757 --> 00:13:11.594
mayn

00:13:11.635 --> 00:13:13.401
mit beyde tekhter.

00:13:14.166 --> 00:13:15.442
eyn tokhter

00:13:16.275 --> 00:13:18.986
hot glaykh khasene gehat, di yingere, Shifre

00:13:21.372 --> 00:13:25.821
mit a bokher vos iz oykh geven in SZCZECIN gelebt in Poyln.

00:13:26.063 --> 00:13:27.409
vayl tsen yor

00:13:27.409 --> 00:13:29.128
hobn mir gelebt in Poyln.

00:13:29.556 --> 00:13:30.529
ven

00:13:31.108 --> 00:13:32.739
zikh ongehoybn

00:13:34.551 --> 00:13:37.633
der, der groyser shtrom in Erets Yisroel

00:13:38.685 --> 00:13:40.096
zaynen ale geforn.

00:13:40.508 --> 00:13:41.430
dan

00:13:42.077 --> 00:13:44.805
iz gekumen a bokher, an oremer bokher

00:13:46.313 --> 00:13:48.602
un arayn in mayn gesheft

00:13:48.726 --> 00:13:50.255
gevorn bakont

00:13:50.363 --> 00:13:51.724
mit der tokhter

00:13:52.135 --> 00:13:55.673
un danken got, funem ershtn tog hobn zey zikh farlibt

00:13:56.218 --> 00:13:57.882
un zey hobn ongehoybn

00:13:58.547 --> 00:13:59.638
arumgeyn

00:13:59.745 --> 00:14:00.906
ober glaykh

00:14:00.906 --> 00:14:03.536
iz er aroysgeforn mit der muter

00:14:04.183 --> 00:14:05.471
in CHOLON

00:14:05.471 --> 00:14:08.210
vayl zeyer a tokhter iz do shoyn geven

00:14:08.858 --> 00:14:10.913
un ikh mit ⟨mayne⟩ tsvey tekhter

00:14:10.913 --> 00:14:12.446
hobn zikh ayngepakt

00:14:12.537 --> 00:14:15.214
un gekumen in Erets Yisroel in CHOLON.

00:14:16.131 --> 00:14:19.196
ikh bin aropgegangen in ⟨LOD⟩. di flign hobn mir

00:14:19.253 --> 00:14:22.422
aroyf mir, ikh bin geven badekt mit shvartse flign.

00:14:22.422 --> 00:14:24.827
vayl ikh bin gekumen fun an ander klimat

00:14:24.827 --> 00:14:27.144
un, un glaykh hobn zey gefilt

00:14:27.285 --> 00:14:28.612
az, az dos iz

00:14:28.315 --> 00:14:29.726
dos iz nisht keyn

00:14:28.635 --> 00:14:31.160
emigrantn fun an ander klimat.

00:14:32.128 --> 00:14:35.338
arayngekumen dort in SOCHNUT. m'hot undz gegebn

00:14:35.338 --> 00:14:37.168
glaykh hob ikh gekusht di erd

00:14:37.168 --> 00:14:39.158
mayne kinder hobn gekusht di erd

00:14:39.158 --> 00:14:41.606
vos mir ayngekumen in der eygener land.

00:14:43.198 --> 00:14:44.832
a simkhe geven.

00:14:44.832 --> 00:14:47.732
zaynen gekumen undzere bakonte un kroyvim

00:14:47.772 --> 00:14:49.723
undz tsugenumen fun ⟨LOD⟩

00:14:49.881 --> 00:14:51.894
arayngezetst in zeyer mashin

00:14:51.894 --> 00:14:53.295
gebrakht aheym.

00:14:53.295 --> 00:14:55.030
di mishpokhe iz nokh haynt

00:14:55.030 --> 00:14:56.930
Smushkin in CHOLON

00:14:58.318 --> 00:14:59.375
Khaim

00:14:59.449 --> 00:15:01.012
un NINE Smushkin

00:15:01.035 --> 00:15:03.155
zey hobn undz oyfgenumen tsu zikh

00:15:03.280 --> 00:15:07.256
un bay zey hob ikh gelebt mit beyde tekhter dray monat.

00:15:07.718 --> 00:15:08.876
di kinder

00:15:08.899 --> 00:15:10.479
zaynen avekgegangen

00:15:10.958 --> 00:15:13.415
in, in a KIBUTS, NEGBA

00:15:14.080 --> 00:15:16.245
lernen di shprakh un arbetn

00:15:16.245 --> 00:15:18.934
un glaykhtsaytik hot men geshikt ot dem

00:15:19.395 --> 00:15:22.477
bokher mit velkhn mayn tokhter iz arumgegangen

00:15:23.108 --> 00:15:24.519
RAFI GOLAN

00:15:25.673 --> 00:15:28.417
zaynen zey ale geven in dem KIBUTS

00:15:28.778 --> 00:15:30.088
a yor tsayt.

00:15:30.280 --> 00:15:31.236
un ikh

00:15:31.512 --> 00:15:33.311
hob glaykh gezukht arbet.

00:15:35.106 --> 00:15:37.192
kh'hob nit gekent zitsn on arbet.

00:15:37.958 --> 00:15:39.895
a gast iz zeyer gut tsu zayn

00:15:39.895 --> 00:15:41.900
ober ikh bin avekgegangen zukhn arbet.

00:15:42.075 --> 00:15:43.486
ikh bin avekgegangen

00:15:47.020 --> 00:15:47.894
in

00:15:47.894 --> 00:15:49.274
shtot rat.

00:15:49.348 --> 00:15:51.708
ikh hob gezogt "ikh vil zukhn arbet.

00:15:51.708 --> 00:15:53.938
ikh bin a mol geven" zog ikh "a lererin

00:15:54.192 --> 00:15:56.110
IVRIT ken ikh a bisl."

00:15:57.212 --> 00:15:58.033
gut.

00:15:58.090 --> 00:16:00.666
hobn zey mir gegebn a poylishe mishpokhe

00:16:02.730 --> 00:16:05.688
heyst az di muter iz geven a poylishe un der foter a yid

00:16:05.688 --> 00:16:07.508
di muter iz geven geshtorbn

00:16:07.508 --> 00:16:08.578
di kinder

00:16:09.241 --> 00:16:10.110
dray

00:16:10.110 --> 00:16:13.963
yesoymim, tsvey n- tekhter un a yingele, nit keyn normaler

00:16:14.678 --> 00:16:17.000
bin ikh gevorn zeyer METAPELET.

00:16:17.732 --> 00:16:20.341
di MASKORET hob ikh bakumen fun IRYA

00:16:20.938 --> 00:16:22.164
fun shtot rat

00:16:22.356 --> 00:16:24.934
un ikh hob opgearbet epes a fir monat.

00:16:24.934 --> 00:16:25.758
fayn.

00:16:26.119 --> 00:16:28.408
Khaim Smushkin zogt "FANYA

00:16:28.633 --> 00:16:31.878
du muzst arayn in Yisroel mit der rekhter fus.

00:16:31.878 --> 00:16:33.659
glaykh hostu bakumen arbet.

00:16:33.659 --> 00:16:36.697
epes a fir fun- hundert funtn a monat hostu."

00:16:36.697 --> 00:16:37.385
fayn.

00:16:38.539 --> 00:16:39.405
do

00:16:39.405 --> 00:16:42.026
hot zikh dervust Zelbst fun Yerusholaim

00:16:42.370 --> 00:16:44.220
geven dan an, an almen

00:16:44.277 --> 00:16:46.667
un er iz oykh fun mayn shtot Disne

00:16:47.618 --> 00:16:51.319
un er hot mir gekent, un mayn man Kasril Fuks hot er gekent

00:16:51.319 --> 00:16:54.244
er iz glaykh gekumen tsu mir tsu forn in CHOLON

00:16:55.397 --> 00:16:57.394
un er hot ⟨dokh⟩ glaykh forgeleygt

00:16:57.394 --> 00:17:00.161
nemen mir tsu zikh in Yerusholaim

00:17:00.161 --> 00:17:01.652
azoy vi ier iz aleyn.

00:17:01.675 --> 00:17:03.275
er hot nit keyn kinder

00:17:03.275 --> 00:17:04.810
hot nit keyn khoyves

00:17:04.810 --> 00:17:06.428
hot an eygene dire.

00:17:06.535 --> 00:17:08.706
er arbet nokh in UNK BONE.

00:17:12.087 --> 00:17:15.236
ikh hob gezen az s'iz geven far mir a tsugepaste zakh.

00:17:15.327 --> 00:17:17.143
kh'hob keyn sakh nit getrakht

00:17:17.233 --> 00:17:19.192
gekumen in Yerusholaim.

00:17:19.192 --> 00:17:20.592
do hobn gelebt

00:17:20.592 --> 00:17:22.779
do hot gelebt Itke Lekekh

00:17:22.887 --> 00:17:24.072
ot di froy

00:17:24.072 --> 00:17:26.642
vos nokh in Disne zayendik vos zi geklapt

00:17:26.642 --> 00:17:29.000
in fentster "kinderlekh, ale antloyft."

00:17:29.000 --> 00:17:31.119
ir hob ikh gefunen in Yerusholaim.

00:17:31.119 --> 00:17:34.339
mit ir gantser mishpokhe mit tekhter mit a zun

00:17:35.593 --> 00:17:38.456
vos zey lebn haynt oykh in Yerusholaim un RECHOVOT

00:17:40.588 --> 00:17:43.130
un do iz gekumen Ayzik Zelbst

00:17:43.677 --> 00:17:44.919
mir zen

00:17:46.090 --> 00:17:49.550
un glaykh hobn zey mir gemakht dem shidekh unter di oygn glaykh

00:17:49.550 --> 00:17:51.510
az dos iz a tsugepaste por

00:17:51.510 --> 00:17:53.020
un ikh bin a raykher froy

00:17:53.020 --> 00:17:54.810
⟨ikh bin⟩ gekumen mit raykhn bagazh

00:17:54.878 --> 00:17:57.086
un er iz zikh an ayngeordnter

00:17:58.560 --> 00:17:59.684
mir hobn gemakht

00:17:59.742 --> 00:18:02.031
a khupe in gikhn in RABANUT

00:18:03.808 --> 00:18:08.527
zaynen geven bakonte undzere vos zaynen geven eydes tsu der khupe.

00:18:11.014 --> 00:18:12.240
eyn tokhter

00:18:12.786 --> 00:18:14.822
afrier hob ikh ir geshtelt a khupe

00:18:15.064 --> 00:18:16.880
bin ikh shoyn geven a farheyrate.

00:18:17.089 --> 00:18:19.867
nakher az mayn tokhter hot khasene gehat

00:18:19.958 --> 00:18:22.213
bin ikh shoyn mit mayn man gegangen

00:18:22.540 --> 00:18:25.422
tsu der khupe fun mayn tokhter, shoyn a farheyrate.

00:18:25.422 --> 00:18:27.680
nit vi mit a khaver bin ikh gegangen.

00:18:31.838 --> 00:18:35.426
in dem zelbn yor hot khasene gehat, dos iz Shifre

00:18:35.972 --> 00:18:38.970
iz Shifre avek lebn mitn man in TSAHALA

00:18:40.208 --> 00:18:42.210
in a dire fun ⟨HAMIDAR⟩

00:18:42.975 --> 00:18:45.605
ikh bin aribergeforn in Yerusholaim

00:18:45.605 --> 00:18:47.915
oyf RECHOV Kleynman vu ikh leb haynt

00:18:48.460 --> 00:18:50.732
un di ⟨fraylin⟩, di tokhter Rekhl

00:18:51.615 --> 00:18:56.519
iz geblibn in der dire vos der SOCHNUT hot tsu undz gegebn far der gantser mishpokhe.

00:18:57.977 --> 00:18:59.422
vi es vayzt oys

00:18:59.462 --> 00:19:02.510
di dire hot keyn sakh glik undz nit gegebn.

00:19:02.635 --> 00:19:05.852
di dire, az me zol gleybn, iz zi geven MAMASH

00:19:06.060 --> 00:19:07.792
mit a, a klole.

00:19:08.085 --> 00:19:10.391
vayl nakher hot zikh aroysgevizn

00:19:11.038 --> 00:19:14.761
in der dire hot mayn tokhter gelebt zeyer veynik.

00:19:16.084 --> 00:19:19.650
zi iz geshtorbn in der dire ven zi iz geven alt

00:19:19.650 --> 00:19:20.988
fertsik yor.

00:19:22.682 --> 00:19:24.228
in toyznt nayn hundert

00:19:24.555 --> 00:19:27.451
finf un akhtsikstn yor iz zi geshtorbn

00:19:27.559 --> 00:19:30.489
ven zi iz gevorn fertsik yor alt. bakumen

00:19:30.489 --> 00:19:32.219
a SARTAN LAVLAV

00:19:32.219 --> 00:19:33.449
un avekgegangen.

00:19:33.449 --> 00:19:36.399
far vos zog ikh az di dire iz nit keyn mazldike?

00:19:37.482 --> 00:19:39.096
vayl in der dire

00:19:39.253 --> 00:19:42.537
hobn gelebt mentshn vos zey hobn zikh glaykh geget

00:19:42.662 --> 00:19:45.153
oder gegete oder glaykh geshtorbn.

00:19:46.611 --> 00:19:48.495
mir hobn zikh dervust nakher.

00:19:49.767 --> 00:19:51.549
vayle nakher hobn ale gezogt

00:19:51.876 --> 00:19:55.312
az di dire iz fun onfang on geven nit keyn mazldike.

00:19:55.116 --> 00:19:58.012
vu iz geven dize dire? ah, in CHOLON.

00:19:56.280 --> 00:19:57.472
in CHOLON.

00:19:58.018 --> 00:19:59.058
in CHOLON.

00:19:59.790 --> 00:20:00.560
yo.

00:20:04.127 --> 00:20:05.960
ober di tokhter RACHEL

00:20:07.266 --> 00:20:12.491
hot gelebt in der dire, in a MIDARsker dire. nakher hot zi di dire opgekoyft

00:20:12.868 --> 00:20:13.790
yo

00:20:14.033 --> 00:20:15.934
far zikh hot zi gehat di dire.

00:20:16.227 --> 00:20:19.376
zi hot gearbet in ⟨MEKOROT⟩ oyf a groysn postn

00:20:21.795 --> 00:20:23.659
ikh hob fun ir a bild, un ikh hob f-

00:20:23.659 --> 00:20:25.869
vos me shraybt vegn ir ven zi iz geshtorbn.

00:20:26.976 --> 00:20:29.619
un der lebn dakht zikh gegangen azoy normal.

00:20:32.123 --> 00:20:35.390
mayn tokhter hot gearbet, un der eydem hot gearbet

00:20:35.751 --> 00:20:38.917
vayl zey zaynen geborn gevorn shoyn in der tsayt tsvey kinder.

00:20:39.463 --> 00:20:41.666
ikh hob mit Ayzik Zelbstn

00:20:41.666 --> 00:20:43.596
gelebt in Yerusholaim.

00:20:43.596 --> 00:20:44.876
er hot gearbet

00:20:44.876 --> 00:20:47.356
nor mir iz geven umedik tsu zitsn

00:20:47.356 --> 00:20:48.789
un gornisht nit ton.

00:20:49.875 --> 00:20:53.424
vi kumt a froy a gezunte etlekhe un fuftsik yor

00:20:53.424 --> 00:20:57.733
tsu zitsn un vartn oyf dem man's parnose? ikh bin geven nit ruik.

00:20:58.431 --> 00:21:01.086
un er hot nit gevelt az ikh zol geyn arbetn

00:21:01.086 --> 00:21:02.579
vayl er hot zikh geshemt

00:21:02.579 --> 00:21:05.084
ot hot er kh- geheyrat, un er shikt

00:21:05.084 --> 00:21:07.194
kloymersht di froy arbetn.

00:21:07.194 --> 00:21:09.534
ober ikh hob gevelt yo geyn arbetn.

00:21:09.534 --> 00:21:12.104
bin ikh gegangen in LISHKAT AVODA

00:21:12.104 --> 00:21:13.590
un BESHUM OFAN

00:21:13.590 --> 00:21:15.950
hot men mir keyn arbet nit gegebn

00:21:18.242 --> 00:21:19.738
khotsh ikh hob geredt

00:21:19.778 --> 00:21:21.521
ikh hob shoyn geredt IVRIT

00:21:21.521 --> 00:21:23.214
nokh fun der heym

00:21:23.794 --> 00:21:24.772
un do

00:21:24.772 --> 00:21:27.832
bin ikh durkhgegangen an ULPAN in CHOLON a halbn yor

00:21:27.832 --> 00:21:33.022
un m'hot mir nit gegebn keyn arbet vos ikh hob gebet in LISHKAT AVODA

00:21:33.022 --> 00:21:34.962
hot men mir nit gegebn.

00:21:35.826 --> 00:21:38.823
biz vanet ikh hob gefunen in a heln frimorgn

00:21:40.652 --> 00:21:41.965
dem MISRAD

00:21:41.965 --> 00:21:43.194
MATAV

00:21:43.386 --> 00:21:47.936
MEM TAV VAV. dos heyst METAPLOT BAYIT.

00:21:48.870 --> 00:21:50.399
do bin ikh arayn

00:21:52.600 --> 00:21:57.150
un do bin ikh geblibn AD hayntikn tog vu ikh arbet nokh

00:21:58.219 --> 00:21:59.975
un oyber m'iz aroys fun dan

00:21:59.975 --> 00:22:01.815
fun dem MISRAD oyf pensye

00:22:01.815 --> 00:22:03.865
bin ikh dortn BEHITNADVUT

00:22:03.865 --> 00:22:06.445
gey ikh arbetn mit kranke mentshn

00:22:07.467 --> 00:22:11.038
mit kranke mentshn gey ikh metapl zayn zikh.

00:22:20.477 --> 00:22:22.448
kh'hob opgearbet in MATAV

00:22:22.448 --> 00:22:26.411
mit kranke mentshn, mit yunge, mit alt, mit farsheydene krenk.

00:22:26.518 --> 00:22:30.174
kh'hob ge- lib gehat di kranke. kh'hob lib gehat di alte.

00:22:30.467 --> 00:22:33.076
kh'hob gebrakht a gute MASKORET in shtub.

00:22:33.808 --> 00:22:37.413
nu, un er hot zikh tsugevoynt az di froy darf aroysgeyn tsu der arbet.

00:22:38.533 --> 00:22:41.871
er iz geven a kranker mentsh, hot gehat a shvakhe harts.

00:22:41.871 --> 00:22:43.921
er hot mir alts gezogt tsu der khasene.

00:22:43.921 --> 00:22:45.641
er hot gehat a hoykhn blutdruk

00:22:45.641 --> 00:22:48.981
ober ikh bin geven a yunge. kh'hob nit farshtanen vos heyst a blutdruk

00:22:48.981 --> 00:22:52.001
vos heyst a kranke harts. ikh bin gekumen fun gezunte

00:22:52.001 --> 00:22:54.541
fun UNK zaynen mir ale geven gezunte

00:22:54.801 --> 00:22:58.179
ober glaykh bin ikh geven zayn METAPELET. kh'hob im glaykh gemakht

00:22:58.179 --> 00:23:00.299
ZIRKOT fun insulin

00:23:01.551 --> 00:23:05.240
un er iz geven gezunt un gearbet akht sho in UNK ⟨BONE⟩

00:23:05.365 --> 00:23:08.150
un ikh volt arbetn biz tsvey, biz dray a zeyger

00:23:08.150 --> 00:23:11.150
un az er volt gekumen fun der arbet iz shoyn geven der mitog

00:23:11.150 --> 00:23:14.890
oyfn tish. ikh hob oysgehit zayn dyete vos er hot gehat diabet

00:23:14.921 --> 00:23:16.791
ikh hob oysgehit di dyete.

00:23:16.791 --> 00:23:18.821
alts iz geven gut un alts iz fayn.

00:23:20.721 --> 00:23:22.149
ober der umglik

00:23:22.155 --> 00:23:23.735
vos mayn tokhter

00:23:25.395 --> 00:23:28.337
iz geshtorbn in elter fun fertsik yor

00:23:28.337 --> 00:23:31.160
dos geyt fun mir nit avek AD HAYOM.

00:23:33.343 --> 00:23:36.982
kh'hob farlorn in mayn lebn di eltern

00:23:37.039 --> 00:23:38.838
brider un shvester

00:23:38.929 --> 00:23:40.323
tsvey mener

00:23:41.055 --> 00:23:44.407
ober ⟨in⟩ mayn Rokhl, di tokhter, dos hot mir shoyn

00:23:45.392 --> 00:23:47.580
in gantsn dershlogn.

00:23:48.514 --> 00:23:49.532
nito

00:23:49.532 --> 00:23:50.820
vos tsu vartn.

00:23:52.665 --> 00:23:54.532
yetst vi iz geshtorbn

00:23:55.467 --> 00:23:57.587
vi iz geshtorbn Zelbst, yo?

00:23:59.871 --> 00:24:00.692
nokh

00:24:03.313 --> 00:24:05.462
ven ikh hob gehat in MATAV

00:24:05.462 --> 00:24:07.358
s'iz geven a fraytik.

00:24:09.085 --> 00:24:13.669
kum ikh aheym fun der arbet un gefin mayn man a toytn oyfn bet.

00:24:14.502 --> 00:24:17.314
er hot bakumen a, a harts atak un geshtorbn.

00:24:18.855 --> 00:24:20.469
inem zelbn tog

00:24:20.796 --> 00:24:23.068
iz er aroys koyfn a tsaytung

00:24:23.158 --> 00:24:26.358
un bagegnt a shkheyne Khaven, do voynt zi noent

00:24:27.833 --> 00:24:29.869
fregt zi bay im "ADON Zelbst

00:24:30.516 --> 00:24:32.985
ir geyt ⟨oyf⟩ bald aroys oyf pensye?" zogt er

00:24:32.985 --> 00:24:38.289
"in dray monatn gey ikh aroys oyf pensye, ober vos vel ikh ton mit mayn erleydike tsayt?"

00:24:41.029 --> 00:24:42.941
er ⟨hot⟩ zeyer geven bazorgt

00:24:42.941 --> 00:24:45.420
vos vet er ton mit zayn erleydike tsayt?

00:24:45.420 --> 00:24:46.830
er iz arayn in shtub

00:24:46.830 --> 00:24:48.364
gevorn im nit gut

00:24:49.180 --> 00:24:50.794
geven aleyn in shtub

00:24:51.407 --> 00:24:53.527
un geshtorbn oyf an ort.

00:24:53.955 --> 00:24:56.007
ikh kum tsu geyn fun der arbet.

00:24:57.600 --> 00:25:00.935
ikh zukh mayn man. er hot gedarft geyn oyf a BRIT MILA

00:25:01.043 --> 00:25:04.699
in dem zelbn hoyz hot er gedarft zayn vu mir zaynen geven ayngeladn.

00:25:04.840 --> 00:25:07.871
ikh efn di tir. di matone iz oyfn tish.

00:25:07.928 --> 00:25:12.613
ikh ze Ayzik iz nito in eyn tsimer, in tsveytn, in dritn. ikh gefin im a teytn.

00:25:14.070 --> 00:25:16.258
dos iz geven mayn tsveytn ⟨heyrung⟩

00:25:16.838 --> 00:25:18.840
fun Yerusholaim.

00:25:18.981 --> 00:25:20.544
haynt leb ikh

00:25:21.090 --> 00:25:22.518
in zayn dire

00:25:22.997 --> 00:25:25.336
vayl er hot mir geshribn a tsavoe

00:25:27.115 --> 00:25:29.103
az di dire blaybt far mir.

00:25:29.103 --> 00:25:31.006
un der UNK blaybt far mir

00:25:31.806 --> 00:25:35.090
emes, er hot gehat a zun adoptirtn

00:25:35.738 --> 00:25:37.757
vos er lebt haynt in HAIFA.

00:25:37.948 --> 00:25:39.714
er heyst DOV ATSMON.

00:25:40.024 --> 00:25:42.617
geven a shpiler in KADUR REGEL

00:25:43.163 --> 00:25:44.034
ober

00:25:45.188 --> 00:25:47.949
ikh hob im oysgetsolt vos zayn kheylek

00:25:48.833 --> 00:25:52.623
loytn din hot zikh gefodert. mir zaynen geblibn gute fraynt

00:25:52.623 --> 00:25:54.693
un ikh bin geblibn lebn

00:25:54.693 --> 00:25:56.302
ot do in der dire

00:25:57.760 --> 00:26:00.049
oyf Kleynman tsvelf

00:26:00.510 --> 00:26:02.630
di dire fir in Yerusholaim

00:26:03.143 --> 00:26:04.183
un vayter

00:26:04.189 --> 00:26:07.845
nokh dem fal hob ikh vayter forgezetst arbetn

00:26:08.391 --> 00:26:12.975
un alts geyt, vayter gegangen der lebn, vayl der lebn muz geyn foroys.

00:26:13.403 --> 00:26:15.118
keyn tsurik iz nito

00:26:15.327 --> 00:26:16.772
un dos iz dos.

00:26:17.605 --> 00:26:19.590
kh'hob opgearbet in MATAV

00:26:20.727 --> 00:26:22.881
kimat zibn un tsvantsik yor

00:26:23.545 --> 00:26:25.912
un aroys oyf pensye mit KAVOD

00:26:25.912 --> 00:26:26.846
fayn.

00:26:27.763 --> 00:26:29.309
un ikh gey haynt

00:26:29.991 --> 00:26:32.139
MAMASH zukhn mitsves

00:26:32.139 --> 00:26:34.575
helfn kranke, helfn oreme

00:26:35.205 --> 00:26:39.451
vayl ikh muz aroysgeyn fun shtub. ikh muz epes oyfton kol zman ikh leb

00:26:41.736 --> 00:26:44.059
un azoy geyt der lebn vayter.

00:26:44.790 --> 00:26:50.656
WOLLEN SIE ah ETWAS NOCH, ETWAS ⟨DATZU⟩ zogn, ah, a maskone, a

00:26:51.270 --> 00:26:53.390
HABEN SIE ETWAS a

00:26:54.544 --> 00:26:55.958
a

00:26:55.958 --> 00:26:58.419
a vuntsh tsu zogn, a vuntsh?

00:26:58.695 --> 00:26:59.499
ye.

00:27:00.552 --> 00:27:02.098
ven, ven

00:27:02.188 --> 00:27:03.734
ven KEREN

00:27:05.091 --> 00:27:06.165
Shpilberg

00:27:06.330 --> 00:27:09.033
Shpigler hot zikh dervust vegn mir

00:27:09.343 --> 00:27:11.159
hobn zey mir forgeleygt

00:27:11.200 --> 00:27:12.561
ikh zol shraybn.

00:27:13.140 --> 00:27:14.923
ikh bin geven zeyer gegn

00:27:15.182 --> 00:27:18.838
vayl ikh hob nor MAMASH nit keyn koykhes tsu shraybn vegn dem.

00:27:18.979 --> 00:27:22.466
mayn avtobiografye iz zeyer a shvere un zeyer a lange.

00:27:22.557 --> 00:27:24.424
kh'hob zey etlekhe mol anzagt

00:27:24.598 --> 00:27:27.832
zaynen gekumen tsu mir ru- rusishe zhurnalistn

00:27:28.092 --> 00:27:30.552
vos ikh volt kenen oyf rusish shraybn zey.

00:27:30.552 --> 00:27:32.682
ikh hob gezogt ikh hob nit keyn koykhes.

00:27:32.682 --> 00:27:34.372
ikh hob naye tsores.

00:27:34.372 --> 00:27:36.292
ikh ken vegn der SHOA

00:27:36.292 --> 00:27:39.105
MAMASH ⟨ikh bin⟩ nit BEKOACH aykh tsu dertseyln.

00:27:39.195 --> 00:27:40.437
nor yetst

00:27:40.512 --> 00:27:43.993
az mir hot ongekumen di GEVERET LIZA

00:27:43.993 --> 00:27:46.766
vos zi hot mir azoy fayn un eydl erklert

00:27:46.789 --> 00:27:50.397
un zi hot mir gezogt az zi, dos iz zeyer a vikhtike zakh

00:27:50.397 --> 00:27:54.529
vos ikh vel alts dermonen vegn der SHOA

00:27:55.092 --> 00:28:00.013
farn kumedikn dor, vet hobn vos tsu dertseyln di dor doyres

00:28:00.272 --> 00:28:02.492
epes iz mir arayn in gedank

00:28:02.492 --> 00:28:05.252
ikh vel prubirn. efsher vel ikh hobn koykhes

00:28:05.252 --> 00:28:06.762
dos tsu dertseyln.

00:28:06.762 --> 00:28:08.572
ober a dank dem ADON

00:28:08.572 --> 00:28:09.902
ELI KULA

00:28:09.902 --> 00:28:11.392
er iz tsu mir gekumen vi a

00:28:11.392 --> 00:28:12.682
vi a psikholog

00:28:13.367 --> 00:28:16.516
un langzam, langzam hot er mir arayngetsoygn

00:28:16.708 --> 00:28:21.174
i- ikh zol dertseyln mayn gantse avtobiografye

00:28:21.265 --> 00:28:25.022
un azoy hobn mir ongefangen, un azoy farendik ikh

00:28:26.125 --> 00:28:29.495
un a dank oyb dos vet ⟨avekgeyn⟩ befeyresh

00:28:29.495 --> 00:28:32.795
far dem nayem dor, vet men hobn vos tsu dertseyln

00:28:33.263 --> 00:28:36.190
az s'iz geven aza Hitler, vos es zaynen umgekumen

00:28:36.190 --> 00:28:37.990
zeks milyon yidn

00:28:37.990 --> 00:28:41.670
nor eyne fun toyznt efsher mit a nes iz geblibn lebn.

00:28:41.670 --> 00:28:44.730
